             was indicted for <rs id="t18320705-230-off1206" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320705-230-off1206" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320705-230-off1206" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18320705-230-cd1207" type="crimeDate">30th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320705-230-off1206 t18320705-230-cd1207"></join>, 9 yards of ribbon, value 12s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320705-230-victim1918" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Newton
                        <interp inst="t18320705-230-victim1918" type="surname" value="Newton"></interp>
